{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6a8d6b0ec8","title":"给军委常委的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"21a6508c87","index":0,"year":1966,"month":3,"day":22,"articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","name":"红旗一九六七年第九期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3ec63011d5","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志给中央重委常委的信","index":0,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"},{"id":"1f727a5f49","type":"paragraph","text":"常卖请同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"},{"id":"fbb3891120","type":"paragraph","text":"送去江青同志召开的部队文艺工作座读会纪要，精阅。这个纪要，经过参加座该会的同志何反复研究，又经过主席三次亲自审阅修改，是一个很好的文件，用毛泽东思想回答了社会主义时期文化革命的许多重大周题，不仅有极大的现实意义而直有深远的历史意义","index":2,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"},{"id":"cf47bd2a6a","type":"paragraph","text":"十六年来，文艺战上存在着失锐的阶级斗章，战胜推的周题还没有解决。文艺这个弹地，无产阶级不去占领，黄产阶级就必然去占领，十等是不可避免的。这是在意藏形态领域里极为广泛、深刻的社会主义革命，搞不好就会出修正主义。我们达须高举毛泽系思想伟大红旗，坚定不移地把这一号羊命进行到底。","index":3,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"},{"id":"66efdbff8c","type":"paragraph","text":"纪要中提出的周题和意见，完全符合部队文艺工作的实际情况，必须坚决贯彻执行，使部队文艺工作在突出政治、促进人的革命化方面起重要作用。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"},{"id":"d3ff5cd11f","type":"paragraph","text":"对纪要有何意见整告，以便报中央审批。","index":5,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"},{"id":"81b9d4cc7f","type":"paragraph","text":"此致敬礼！","index":6,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"},{"id":"2e7a115d43","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪","index":7,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"},{"id":"21f38d05c8","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年三月二十二日","index":8,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8"}],"page":{"id":"4c93dfc589","publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"6a8d6b0ec8","start":12,"end":12}}}},"__N_SSG":true}